                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="cap" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Figure 4.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Dispatcher pipeline. The rhombus is a synchronous decision: a positive Lookup short-circuits the Kafka&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;offset commit and avoids spending an RPC on already-joined clicks.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Transient failures (throttle, network,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;joiner not ready) re-enter the pipeline through an in-process DelayQueue with exponential backoff, capped&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 18px; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;at 10 attempts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;" parent="1" vertex="1">
